chart.title: En-route HFE (Actual) time series
chart.description: Time series of the average value and distribution of the Horizontal Flight Efficiency indicator of the actual route. The average value is obtained from the division of the effective distance flown between the actual flown length in a certain entity. The quartiles and median values are calculated from the daily average values of the indicator.
